description: You can ask about characters from popular TV shows and movies. We currently support characters from Game of Thrones, Breaking Bad, Paw Patrol, My Little Pony and Peppa pig. We are continuing to add more characters as we go along. To use the skill you need an account on https://www.starfishmint.com/audio. You also need to have a subscription for Starfish skills
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask starfish peeps who is Walter
Alexa, ask starfish peeps who is Sansa Stark
Alexa, ask starfish peeps who is Pinkie Pie
name: Starfish Peeps
shortDescription: You can ask all about characters from popular TV shows.
